Handlers and event definitions for events triggered by Rhizosphere visualizations.

Class Summary
ErrorEvent Event to notify that one or more visualization errors have occurred on the visualization, or have been cleared from it.
FilterEvent Event to notify that the filtering criteria of a Rhizosphere visualization have changed.
LayoutEvent Event to notify that a layout operation occurred on a Rhizosphere visualization.
ModelChangeEvent Event to notify that one or more RhizosphereModel have been added or removed from the visualization.
ReadyEvent Event to notify that a Rhizosphere visualization has completed initialization is ready for user interaction.
SelectionEvent Event to notify that a selection operation occurred on a Rhizosphere visualization.
